&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3（MC）<BR>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 4（SC）<BR><BR>8（左侧戒指） &nbsp; 0（AC）<BR>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1（MAC）<BR>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2（DC）<BR>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3（MC）<BR>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 4（SC）<BR><BR>10(腰带)0（AC）<BR>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1（MAC）<BR>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2（DC）<BR>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3（MC）<BR>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 4（SC）<BR><BR>11(鞋)&nbsp;&nbsp; 0（AC）<BR>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1（MAC）<BR>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2（DC）<BR>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3（MC）<BR>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 4（SC）<BR><BR>12(宝石)0（AC）<BR>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1（MAC）<BR>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2（DC）<BR>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3（MC）<BR>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 4（SC）<BR><BR>@改属性 12 2 1<BR>12指的是宝石.2指的是攻击.1指的是加一点</FONT></SPAN> \r\n<!-- Baidu Button BEGIN -->', 1385702290, 0, '游戏里面超级制造的详细说明', 3),
